{"tid":1589342,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本港將舉行多項活動慶祝支那國慶70周年","createTime":"2019-09-23T08:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T08:58:02.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e257845b79e9671ce4bfcb241493ab938c808378","tid":1589342,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:48:15.000Z","msg":"本港將於十月一日舉行連串活動，慶祝中華人民共和國成立七十周年。除了早上舉行的升旗儀式暨國慶酒會，「幻彩詠香江」燈光音樂匯演，亦會在十月重新編排，在LED屏幕展示慶祝國慶的元素。<br />\n<br />\n香港郵政將於國慶日以「中華人民共和國成立七十周年」為題，發行一套四枚郵票及一張郵票小型張，各區的主要街道、政府建築物外牆、政府場地及口岸，將由本周開始陸續懸掛慶祝國慶燈柱彩旗及橫額。"},{"pid":"cf16b11225607a92861e01cc0b677961194d8959","tid":1589342,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:48:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1176456&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1176456%26csid%3D261_341&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK6xZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=c4f5154f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1176456&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"f051d1c92c1331b072f3563c5a4807e79169fd5e","tid":1589342,"uid":54181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:49:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a5dd435e55b471e6e8243ff92743b843ec3e241","tid":1589342,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:53:30.000Z","msg":"支持香港政府用鐳射槍慶祝中国国庆"},{"pid":"9808423fe595478a1191d775e5c6f6deef76d2b4","tid":1589342,"uid":235465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:54:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">早上舉行的升旗儀式</span><br />\n無人機衝鋒/鐳射筆狂照有無機"},{"pid":"b13ccbd583d3b9c8ece2c018dfbf8642064b5d19","tid":1589342,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T08:58:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多